==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Safeness
<hw>Safe"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
safe; freedom from hazard, danger, harm, or loss; safety; security; as
the <xex>safeness</xex> of an experiment, of a journey, or of a
possession.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

